name: <range::Range<usize> as slice::GetDisjointMutIndex>::is_overlapping

convert::From::from.doc: Converts to this type from the input type.

slice::GetDisjointMutIndex::is_overlappi.doc:
Returns `true` if `self` overlaps with `other`.

 Note that we don't consider zero-length ranges to overlap at the beginning or the end,
 but do consider them to overlap in the middle.
